cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI

This paper deals with privacy concerns in cloud-hosted inference of deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also proposes a method for reducing the information content of communicated data while maintaining accuracy, which falls under the category of machine learning. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper uses deep neural networks for experimentation, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and system security (cs.SI).
